# Calendar UI

A modern, responsive calendar web application built with React, Tailwind CSS, and Vite.  
Features include event creation, editing, deletion, conflict detection, search, date range filtering, and dark mode.

## Features

- Month view calendar with event display
- Add, edit, and delete events with color coding
- Conflict detection for overlapping events
- Sidebar with:
  - Mini calendar
  - Date navigation
  - Monthly/yearly and date range event filters
  - Search events by title
  - Today's reminders
- Responsive design and dark mode toggle

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v16 or newer recommended)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) (comes with Node.js)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone <repo-url>
   cd calendar-ui

2. Install dependencies:
    npm install

Development
3. Start the development server:
    npm run dev

Open http://localhost:5173 in your browser.   